  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile, pending signature)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package conforms to the Minimal profile; a hash is provided for content integrity but the digital signature is absent pending completion of the institutional signature workflow. Full 13-factor assessment is included. Decision: Accepted with conditions documented in the decision record.",
