    "rationale": "Package accepted under Minimal profile with conditions. Seven of thirteen credibility factors were formally assessed; all achieved levels fall below required levels for MRL 5. Six factors were flagged as epistemic gaps. The assessment team accepts this package as a complete documentation of the credibility gap inventory, with the understanding that the identified deficiencies must be remediated before regulatory submission. Digital signature is pending completion of the institutional DocuSign workflow; package integrity is maintained via the sha256 hash. The absence of a signature does not affect the credibility gap findings documented herein.",
